info:
  title: Territorial Division RESTful API
  description: This is the Dominican Republic territorial division from the ONE.
  version: v1
  contact:
    name: OGTIC
    url: https://ogtic.gob.do
    email: info@ogtic.gob.do
tags: []
servers: []
components:
  schemas:
    ResponseRegionDto:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        code:
          type: string
        identifier:
          type: string
    BadRequest:
      type: object
      properties:
        statusCode:
          type: number
          default: 400
        message:
          type: string
        timestamp:
          format: date-time
          type: string
      required:
        - statusCode
        - message
        - timestamp
    BadRequestResponseDto:
      type: object
      properties:
        valid:
          type: boolean
          default: false
        BadRequest:
          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/BadRequest"
      required:
        - valid
        - BadRequest
    NotFoundResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        statusCode:
          type: number
          default: 404
        message:
          type: string
        timestamp:
          format: date-time
          type: string
      required:
        - statusCode
        - message
        - timestamp
    NotFoundResponseDto:
      type: object
      properties:
        valid:
          type: boolean
          default: false
        data:
          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/NotFoundResponse"
      required:
        - valid
        - data
    ResponseProvinceDto:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        code:
          type: string
        identifier:
          type: string
        regionCode:
          type: string
    ResponseMunicipalityDto:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        code:
          type: string
        identifier:
          type: string
        provinceCode:
          type: string

          type: string
    ResponseDistrictDto:

      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        code:
          type: string
        identifier:
          type: string
        municipalityCode:
          type: string
